    <Title><![CDATA[Download gallery widget]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>The download gallery widget provides a way to select VFS resources from galleries, or upload new resources into galleries.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
